10 Using Ciao inside GNU emacs
******************************

*Author(s):* Manuel Hermenegildo, Manuel C. Rodriguez, Daniel Cabeza,
, The Computational logic, Languages, , Implementation, and
Parallelism (CLIP) Group, <webmaster@clip.dia.fi.upm.es>,
