160 Unweighted graph-processing utilities
*****************************************

*Author(s):* M. Carlsson, adapted from shared code written by Richard
A O'Keefe. Mods by F.Bueno and M.Carro..

   *Version:* 1.10#7 (2006/4/26, 19:22:13 CEST)

